des:
Are you a huge Dallas Cowboys fan? Then you need the Dallas Football Flash Briefing Skill by FanSided to get the latest news, opinions and rumors on your Cowboys. 

The Landry Hat is the Dallas Cowboys news and opinions site brought to you by the FanSided Network. The Landry Hat is dedicated to providing top-notch Cowboys news, views, and original content. This site also serves as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
